game.name: Spider Fly
game.description:
This time you do not have a plane to fly in the high sky, but a cute and little Spiderman baby which also has its own flying dream. Do you think that you can manage this brand new adventure challenge perfectly? Join Spider Fly game and be prepared to help your favorite spider superhero fly, jump and crash different types of magic enemies! We know that the space is full of enemies, but you are also skilled enough to get your plane through all the hurdles. 
The best part is that the controls of the game are pretty clear and simple. This means that anybody can try it out without bothering about its complexities. Put your finger on your mouse and hold and release it to move your character upward and downward while avoiding the obstacles. Make sure to collect as many stars as you can to give your final score a deserving boost. More coins you grab, the higher score you will be able to make in this free online flying game. 
You can also use those coins to upgrade your spider superhero and improve his power. Be focused and try to reach all goals and accomplish all 99 highly interesting and challenging missions in this cool html5 jumping game! If you get bored, feel free to play other fly games on atmegame.com. The good news is that you do not have to download app or software to play our jumping games in your device. Good luck to find the most interesting jump puzzle for free!!
